{"tid":2068400,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"梁錦祥：今次中美會面時間好短，只是各自表述立場。 預計國安法照常立法！","createTime":"2020-06-17T15:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T05:52:53.000Z","uid":219007,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a7d7b1c0c086999980c5f276ed20515a5f3a9e7d","tid":2068400,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:55:16.000Z","msg":"梁錦祥賓州時事：<br />\n<br />\n今次蓬佩奧同楊潔篪見面時間仲短過金正恩同侵<br />\n<br />\n而蓬佩奧逗留夏威夷嘅時間都只係得一日<br />\n<br />\n換言之佢哋應該唔會有好深入嘅討論，只係各自表述自己<br />\n<br />\n立場，似發表聲明多於達成共識，即係今次唔去談判。<br />\n<br />\n完咗之後就各自做嘢，國安法照常上馬。"},{"pid":"6adf31de8d77aa0fd648bcb6c75e13459ce5d218","tid":2068400,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"梁錦祥<span style=\"color: red;\">一週</span>時事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58270748c45f439480a9d6551c8055ee3baab53a","tid":2068400,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"Ok, go ahead"},{"pid":"aa9f7737bef42ec6b41f3e4095713feb5896a665","tid":2068400,"uid":78662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:56:46.000Z","msg":"幾時放重溫😪無聽到"},{"pid":"31e330ed0fc1ccce95abb06f19157e9888605f35","tid":2068400,"uid":90556,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:57:50.000Z","msg":"中共點會縮"},{"pid":"7bb0434bb43d7d554a9564ca136a2403141fa289","tid":2068400,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31e330ed0fc1ccce95abb06f19157e9888605f35","tid":2068400,"uid":90556,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:57:50.000Z","msg":"中共點會縮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T15:58:18.000Z","msg":"會縮都應該一年半載後<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90cbf2ed5b63bbf909df6d53c1ea1b3484601d0","tid":2068400,"uid":51583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"